---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
import SectionsLayout from '../layouts/SectionsLayout.astro';
import CardDeck from '../components/CardDeck.astro'
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import LongCard from '../components/LongCard.astro';
---

<Layout title="Fonzies site">
	<main>
		<Navigation/>
		<Hero title='Alfonso Garibay' subtitle="Developer & Designer"/>
		
		<SectionsLayout title='about me' custom=''>
			<div class="flex flex-wrap max-md:max-w-xs max-md:text-center ">
				<div class="w-full sm:w-1/2">
				
				<div class="font-header text-8xl max-md:text-2xl ">
					<ul class="content-center">
					<li id="enthusiastic" class="hover:scale-150 transition-transform duration-300 hover:rotate-3 hover:text-pink-400">Enthusiastic </li>
					<li id="developer" class="hover:scale-150 transition-transform duration-300 hover:rotate-2 hover:text-blue-400">developer </li>
					<li id="designer" class="hover:scale-150 transition-transform duration-300  hover:rotate-3 hover:text-red-400">designer </li>
					<li id="versatile" class="hover:scale-150 transition-transform duration-300 hover:rotate-2 hover:text-yellow-400">versatile </li>
					<li id="adventurous" class="hover:scale-150 transition-transform duration-300 hover:rotate-3 hover:text-green-400">Adventurous </li>  
					</ul>
				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 ">
				
					<p id="description" class="font-nonheader text-4xl max-md:text-sm ">
						Hey there, I'm Alfonso, but you can call me Fonzie. 
						<span class="text-pink-300 hover:rotate-3">
						I'm all about design, development, and helping people establish 
						their online presence. 
						</span>
						
						With a background in 
						computer engineering, I've honed my skills in both 
						hardware and software development, though these days 

						<span class="text-blue-300">
						I primarily focus on web development. 
						</span>
						
						<span class="text-yellow-300">
						I've also dabbled
						in native iOS development
						</span>

						, which has added to my versatility.
						When it comes to design, 
						<span class="text-red-300">
						I'm a big fan of Figma, and I find 
						immense joy in crafting beautiful interfaces.
						</span>

						<span class="text-green-300">
						Oh, and did I 
						mention that I'm an avid traveler? Exploring different places 
						and uncovering the common threads that connect us all is 
						something I truly cherish.
						</span>
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</SectionsLayout>

		<SectionsLayout title='Skills & Training' custom='bg-slate-890'>
			<div class="flex flex-wrap max-md:max-w-xs">
				<div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 text-right flex flex-col gap-2 ">
					<div class="border-green-400 border-4 p-2 rounded-lg w-fit text-left max-md:min-w-full">
						<h2 class="text-6xl text-green-400 font-header ">Languages</h2>
						<ul class="text-4xl">
							<li>🇺🇸 English</li>
							<li>🇪🇸 Español</li>
							<li>🇮🇹 Italiano</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					
					<div class="border-yellow-400 border-4 p-2 rounded-lg w-fit text-left">
						<h2 class="text-6xl text-yellow-400 font-header">Skills</h2>
						<ul class="text-4xl ">
							<li>📱 iOS mobile developement</li>
							<li>🖥️ Full-stack web development</li>
							<li>🎨 Web Design </li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					
					<div class="border-blue-400 border-4 p-2 rounded-lg w-fit text-left">
						<h2 class="text-6xl text-blue-400 font-header">Education</h2>
						<ul class="text-4xl">
							<li>🎓 Computer Engineering, SJSU B.S.</li>
							<li>🏅iOS Development, CodePath Honors Cert</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 flex justify-end max-md:hidden"> 
					<img 
						src="https://github.com/AlfonsoGaribay/AlfonsoGaribay.github.io/blob/Astro-branch/src/imgs/portrait-alt-min.png?raw=true" 
						alt="profile" 
						class="rounded-full border-pink-400 border-solid border-4 aspect-square"
					>
				</div>
			</div>
		</SectionsLayout>

		<SectionsLayout title='Works' custom=''>
			<div class="flex justify-center flex-col gap-4 ">
				<CardDeck/>
				
				<LongCard 
					title='LexiJane Bakery' 
					subtitle="Design" 
					keyWords={['Redesign','something','other','whatnot']}
					imgUrl='https://github.com/AlfonsoGaribay/AlfonsoGaribay.github.io/blob/Astro-branch/src/imgs/LexiJane-min.png?raw=true'
					linkTo='https://www.figma.com/proto/WBtklPScPajjOO5Aqh2vVY/Design-System%3A-LexiJane-Bakery?page-id=0%3A1&type=design&node-id=130-1156&viewport=1416%2C1659%2C0.18&scaling=min-zoom&starting-point-node-id=130%3A1156&show-proto-sidebar=1'
					custom=''
					>
					I undertook a redesign project for a local business in a neighboring city, 
							focusing on enhancing user-friendliness and aesthetics. By carefully analyzing 
							the existing layout, I made strategic adjustments to improve usability while maintaining 
							familiarity for a seamless transition. Through the refinement of the layout, introduction 
							of a new color palette, and consistent design elements, I created a cohesive and visually 
							engaging experience. Working closely with the client, I ensured their preferences were 
							incorporated into the final design. The client was delighted with the outcome, which 
							successfully combined user-friendly functionality and an appealing aesthetic. Stay tuned 
							for the upcoming deployment of this exciting project, showcasing my passion for creating 
							exceptional user experiences.
				</LongCard>

				<LongCard 
					title='LexiJane Bakery' 
					subtitle="Design" 
					keyWords={['Redesign','something','other','whatnot']}
					imgUrl='https://github.com/AlfonsoGaribay/AlfonsoGaribay.github.io/blob/Astro-branch/src/imgs/LexiJane-min.png?raw=true'
					linkTo='https://www.figma.com/proto/WBtklPScPajjOO5Aqh2vVY/Design-System%3A-LexiJane-Bakery?page-id=0%3A1&type=design&node-id=130-1156&viewport=1416%2C1659%2C0.18&scaling=min-zoom&starting-point-node-id=130%3A1156&show-proto-sidebar=1'
					custom='flex-row-reverse'
					>
					I undertook a redesign project for a local business in a neighboring city, 
							focusing on enhancing user-friendliness and aesthetics. By carefully analyzing 
							the existing layout, I made strategic adjustments to improve usability while maintaining 
							familiarity for a seamless transition. Through the refinement of the layout, introduction 
							of a new color palette, and consistent design elements, I created a cohesive and visually 
							engaging experience. Working closely with the client, I ensured their preferences were 
							incorporated into the final design. The client was delighted with the outcome, which 
							successfully combined user-friendly functionality and an appealing aesthetic. Stay tuned 
							for the upcoming deployment of this exciting project, showcasing my passion for creating 
							exceptional user experiences.
				</LongCard>
			</div>
		</SectionsLayout>

		


		<Footer/>
	</main>
</Layout>


